graphs.text: #   The leaves and overall shape of plant [3,3] resemble those of
# plant [1,1] - dark leaves with white teeth, dark root
# plant [1,2] - light flower, dark curled leaves, dark root
# plant [1,3] - many dark leaves, dark roots
# plant [1,4] - dark leaves on right side of stem only
# plant [2,1] - light inflorescene or berries, dark round leaves, light root
# plant [2,2] - many small dark leaves, light roots
# plant [2,3] - dark knobby leaves, dark root
# plant [2,4] - dark bushy leaves, slplayed roots
# plant [2,5] - dark bushy leaves, light cauliflower, light stem
# plant [3,1] - dark leaves, light stem, dark base, light roots
# plant [3,2] - many dark leaves, light edge
# plant [3,3] - dark pine-like leaves, light roots
# plant [3,4] - very large dark leaf, light roots
